{"id":"5aab47cf-dcad-4c75-af73-d8b47e598011","name":"The Only Way Out is Through","description":"<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Overview</strong></h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The group was attacked a few days ago by some riders in their camp, these are the ones that managed to escape.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 3);\">Sabrina </span>- Driven solely by logic and survival; seeking a permanent sanctuary.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 100, 230);\">Amelia </span>- Highly effective fighter with melee weapons, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">whose mind has broken as a defense mechanism against the trauma</mark></span><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 54, 23);\">Carlos</span><span style=\"color: rgb(15, 243, 123);\"> </span>- Former military <mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">chef</mark>, he's trying to help anyone he can, even risking his own health, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">currently infected by a bite.</mark></span></p><p></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 107, 255);\"><strong>Huge thanks to </strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"chakra-link css-spn4bz\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/a9132455-0b63-45af-a9a2-9815e5397b69_profile-of-nicholas-cs\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(1, 106, 255);\"><strong>@NicholasCS</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 107, 255);\"><strong> </strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 107, 255);\"><strong>for making the images of this bot, bot wouldn't be here without him</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 107, 255);\"><strong>Special thanks to </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(1, 106, 255);\"><strong>@</strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/7aee9c33-334c-4b43-a297-fcdaef6e025c_profile-of-zappy-jet\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(1, 106, 255);\"><strong>ZappyJet</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(1, 106, 255);\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 107, 255);\"><strong>for making a huge part of the 1st and 2nd intro</strong></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Opening messages</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">They just escaped a raid / attack to their camp</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p><strong>Intro 1 </strong>- YOU are their leader / friend / part of the group that survived the raider attack</p><p><strong>intro 2 </strong>- YOU can be a raider that caught up to them (evil POV?), the first part of the message is the same as the first one (so you don't double read the same thing)</p><p><strong>Intro 3 </strong>- YOU are a random survivor that happened to stump into them.... you could also be a zombie? idk if you are into that kinda pov, but if you are go for it, this is the more open scenario</p><p><strong>Intro 4</strong> - Nothing, do whatever you want, the world is a canvas or smth like that</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Images of them</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Sabrina</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/p_-9nrLrgAU5-8boc1R1V.webp\" style=\"width: 277px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Amelia</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/doJ8R4gd6iHWkuqJPU3LE.webp\" style=\"width: 281px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p></p><hr><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.3rem; color: rgb(195, 0, 255);\"><strong>The CAP-29 Apocalypse</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><st","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"VLMHykIx5MbUF_qLg5eIg.webp","creator":"_Taka_","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","👩‍🦰 Female","👭 Multiple","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","🔦 Horror"],"chats":4522,"messages":96331,"created_at":"2025-12-11T23:29:34.622770+00:00"}